{
  "stem": "7506.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as I say, our warmth, I think, was a lot helped by our physical strength at that time to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it's terribly cold, terribly cold in the winter in that part of Holland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you have covers on the bunks?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all had like what one would call a gray army blanket.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we'd been given one each, because we didn't bring any blankets with us, only our rucksack and our shoulder bag.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had no bedding with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We only had our clothes with us that we were able to take and that we were allowed to take.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think there were certain things allowed to be taken, and not allowed to be taken.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as most Dutch citizens those days were very law abiding, I think we all did what we were told.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, I think, left Westerbork in 2nd or 3rd of January, 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we, believe it or not, were put in passenger cars, passenger rail cars, with the blinds drawn down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What did you think?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought at the time, it was strange.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Other people had been taken in transports in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why are we going in an ordinary train like I'd been used to as a child?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I personally thought we were going to go either to a neutral country, or they were going to take us to England.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never thought we were going to a bad place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I thought we were lucky to be in those trains and not in the others which I had seen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The train left, and we traveled in the night, in the dark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It stopped a few times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We could carefully open a little thing you pulled out, which were all pulled out.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
